---
import Tipsntricks from "./tipsntricks.astro"
---


<section class="video-wrapper">
  <div class="mirco-service-video-wrapper">
    <div class="mirco-service-cta-wrapper">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          Today, ads often fall flat because people are pros at ignoring them.
          They've gotten really good at tuning out anything that screams "buy
          me!" We take a different approach, inspired by the best content
          creators out there.
        </p>
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          We craft content that feels real and genuine, so the message actually
          sticks. And, more importantly, it helps build a connection with the
          people watching. We mix storytelling and visuals to create content
          that is true to the brand and adds value for the viewer.
        </p>
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          Our mission is to shake up the way businesses advertise. We're all
          about growing organically and having real conversations with your
          community. We use strategies tailored to each brand, helping them
          reach and connect with their audience on a deeper level.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper">
        <a
          class="mirco-service-cta-button"
          target=”_blank”
          href="https://app.formbricks.com/s/clzu6zoe50000c8nkwg15thwb">Get in touch</a
        >
      </div>
      <Tipsntricks/>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
   @font-face {
    font-family: "goudy_bookletter_1911";
    src: url("/font.woff") format("woff");
  }
  .video-wrapper {
    background-color: #101010;
    color: #fffbef;
    height: auto;
    width: 100vw;
    max-width: 100vw;
    padding-bottom: 5vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    /* padding-top: 5vh; */
    /* background-image: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      hsl(241deg 100% 64%) 0%,
      hsl(241deg 100% 64%) 33%,
      hsl(254deg 95% 75%) 67%,
      hsl(45deg 100% 97%) 100%
    ); */
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 20px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mirco-service-video-wrapper {
    height: 90%;
    padding: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 1vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: top;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-heading {
    font-family: "goudy_bookletter_1911";
    color: #07005c;
  }

  .two {
    color: #fffbef;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-wrapper {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    border: none;
    background-color: #fffbef;
    color: #101010;
    font-size: 20px;
    width:fit-content;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 50px 10px 50px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
  
  }

  .wrapper {
    max-width: 45ch;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 580px) {
    .mirco-service-cta-wrapper {
      font-size: 2rem;
      max-width: 55ch;
    }
    .mirco-service-video-wrapper {
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .mirco-service-cta-button {
      width: 200px;
    }
    .mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-bottom: 5vh;
    }
  }
</style>
